11:16.968 --> 11:18.261
- Oh, my God!
- Jesus, Jesus!

11:18.261 --> 11:20.263
Wesley, why are you naked
under that?

11:20.263 --> 11:21.848
I thought we all were.

11:21.848 --> 11:24.601
Hey, guys. Take a seat.

11:24.601 --> 11:29.773
So now you have seen
the Sandbox revolution.

11:29.773 --> 11:33.860
We here at Sandbox believe
that we can no longer afford

11:33.860 --> 11:36.613
to keep our heads in the sand.

11:36.613 --> 11:39.199
Chase,
I don't need the whole pitch.

11:39.199 --> 11:41.743
Truth is, I think
your technology is a little,

11:41.743 --> 11:44.496
um, hmm--what is the word
that I am looking for?

11:44.496 --> 11:46.164
- Bogus?
- What's a nicer way

11:46.164 --> 11:48.416
- of saying that?
- Hmm. Uh, spurious?

11:48.416 --> 11:50.543
Spurious. Great, spurious.

11:50.543 --> 11:54.339
The tech is spurious, but you
and Wesley are old friends,

11:54.339 --> 11:58.134
so how 'bout we throw you
50 grand for, I don't know,

11:58.134 --> 11:59.469
20%, a million percent?

11:59.469 --> 12:01.262
We're all havin' fun here.
[light laughter]

12:01.262 --> 12:03.348
- $50,000?
- Uh-huh.

12:03.348 --> 12:05.517
Well, um,

12:05.517 --> 12:09.729
