but we believe our valuation

12:09.729 --> 12:11.690
to be at 5 billion.

12:11.690 --> 12:12.732
I'm sorry.

12:12.732 --> 12:14.359
I might've gotten sand
in my ears.

12:14.359 --> 12:16.653
Did you say "billion" with a B?

12:16.653 --> 12:19.656
We believe that
with our tech,

12:19.656 --> 12:22.033
we should be able
to garner a significant share--

12:22.033 --> 12:23.785
What tech? You have no tech.

12:23.785 --> 12:26.663
You have the idea
of batteries made out of sand,

12:26.663 --> 12:28.456
which is really just
a couple letters away

12:28.456 --> 12:30.250
from batteries made out
of farts.

12:32.043 --> 12:34.504
Well...

12:34.504 --> 12:36.006
thank you for your interest.

12:36.006 --> 12:38.049
Well, thank you so much
for showing us around.

12:38.049 --> 12:40.468
This has been hilarious,

12:40.468 --> 12:43.513
