12:46.975 --> 12:48.601
Of course not, Wesley.

12:48.601 --> 12:50.228
At least not initially.

12:50.228 --> 12:53.690
Hey, um,
can I have your email?

12:53.690 --> 12:56.276
Oh, I would,
but I don't have email.

12:56.276 --> 12:57.819
[laughs]

12:57.819 --> 13:00.363
Oh, I just--this is just--
I check the weather on this.

13:00.363 --> 13:02.699
- That's just for my weather.
- Oh, okay.

13:02.699 --> 13:04.826
Well, I'm sorry
it didn't work out.

13:04.826 --> 13:06.828
I felt a real connection
with you,

13:06.828 --> 13:09.122
