than with the Tesla people.

13:09.122 --> 13:12.709
With the Tes--Tesla.

13:12.709 --> 13:14.878
Huh.

13:14.878 --> 13:16.838
Bet you would've invested
if Cyrus had asked you to.

13:16.838 --> 13:19.257
- Cyrus knows things.
- It's true. I do.

13:19.257 --> 13:20.925
And this place
is super sketchy.

13:20.925 --> 13:23.219
Yeah, I can't believe Tesla's
looking at them.

13:23.219 --> 13:25.013
How do you know Tesla's
looking at them?

13:25.013 --> 13:26.890
The creepy engineer told me.

13:26.890 --> 13:29.309
Weird, Tesla usually has
pretty good instincts

13:29.309 --> 13:30.268
about this stuff.

13:30.268 --> 13:31.686
