18:25.271 --> 18:26.731
Dustin held his wrist
by my face

18:26.731 --> 18:28.316
for an entire TED Talk,
and it smelled.

18:28.316 --> 18:30.276
- It was a smelly wrist.
- Are we sure

18:30.276 --> 18:31.945
this isn't a scam? If--

18:31.945 --> 18:34.781
in my class, we were reading
about irrational exuberance.

18:34.781 --> 18:36.491
[sighs] It's not a textbook, Jack.

18:36.491 --> 18:38.118
- It says the basic--
- We're buds and all--

18:38.118 --> 18:40.495
