seriously embarrassing yourself

18:40.495 --> 18:42.455
- right now.
- Machine learning can--

18:42.455 --> 18:44.457
Guys, this is amazing,
everything you're doing

18:44.457 --> 18:46.334
- with sensors.
- Uh, you mean AI?

18:46.334 --> 18:47.669
Yeah, whatever. AI.

18:47.669 --> 18:49.421
We're gonna need
to discuss this for a minute.

18:49.421 --> 18:51.214
Sure. Mm-hmm.

18:51.214 --> 18:52.340
We need the room.

18:52.340 --> 18:53.675
Oh! Okay.

18:53.675 --> 18:55.343
Yeah, so we're gonna have to...

18:55.343 --> 18:57.470
[shooing]

18:57.470 --> 18:59.764
[door slams]
Wesley, get Chase on the phone.

18:59.764 --> 19:01.057
- Now?
- Uh, yeah.

19:01.057 --> 19:02.142
I am not gonna lose Sandbox,

19:02.142 --> 19:03.935
and I cannot sit
through another minute

19:03.935 --> 19:06.521
of these nerds
and their stupid, boring pitch.

19:06.521 --> 19:08.023
Sensors this, sensors that.

19:08.023 --> 19:09.149
<i>[bleep] get laid.</i>

19:09.149 --> 19:10.859
<i>[line trilling]</i>

19:10.859 --> 19:13.069
