19:21.327 --> 19:23.038
Uh, look,
we're upping our offer.

19:23.038 --> 19:25.165
5%, $300 million.

19:25.165 --> 19:26.833
And if you want, we'll throw in
that cute little blonde

19:26.833 --> 19:28.001
that your engineer likes
so much.

19:28.001 --> 19:29.627
[laughs]

19:29.627 --> 19:31.755
