19:51.983 --> 19:55.570
to a bunch
of dumb, smelly virgins

19:55.570 --> 19:57.906
talking about sensors nonstop.

19:57.906 --> 19:59.407
It's AI.

19:59.407 --> 20:01.659
And yeah, maybe Katherine
came off as kind of a bitch,

20:01.659 --> 20:03.328
- but...
- [clears throat]

20:03.328 --> 20:04.829
If you get to know her,

20:04.829 --> 20:07.874
you'll realize that A,
she's also low-key kind of hot,

20:07.874 --> 20:11.252
and B, she's the bitch you want
on your side

20:11.252 --> 20:12.879
because she sticks by you.

20:12.879 --> 20:14.673
