the going gets rough,

20:26.935 --> 20:30.480
we're the ones you want next
to you in that sandbox.

20:32.899 --> 20:35.694
- [all cheering]
- Yeah, to Sandbox

20:35.694 --> 20:37.153
- and to Wesley...
- Oh.

20:37.153 --> 20:38.405
For making it all happen.

20:38.405 --> 20:40.156
In the future,
I am gonna listen to you more,

20:40.156 --> 20:42.492
- or, you know, at least try to.
<i>- Danke.</i>

20:42.492 --> 20:43.910
Oh, looks like
the news leaked.

20:43.910 --> 20:46.079
Our share price is already
shooting up pre-market.

20:46.079 --> 20:47.163
- Whoo!
- Yes!

20:47.163 --> 20:48.748
- [laughs] Suck it, board.
- [laughs]

20:48.748 --> 20:50.917
